## Section Guidelines

### Key Discussion Points
- 3-5 bullets maximum
- Focus on decisions, updates, and important context
- Avoid sensitive/confidential items unless appropriate

### Action Items
- Clear, specific, actionable
- Include deadlines if discussed
- Separate "theirs" vs "mine" for accountability

### Personal Touch (Optional)
Use when appropriate:
- "Good luck with [certification/exam]!"
- "Congrats on [personal milestone]!"
- "Hope [event] goes well!"
- "Enjoy your [PTO/trip]!"

Avoid when:
- Topic is too personal
- Could be misinterpreted
- Doesn't fit the relationship

### Sign-off Options
| Tone | Sign-off |
|------|----------|
| Casual | "Talk soon," / "Thanks!" / "Cheers," |
| Formal | "Best regards," / "Thank you," |
| Brief | "Thanks!" / "-[Name]" |

